&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a Digital Media Specialist with 2+ years’ experience who’s ready to move beyond campaign delivery and help shape how digital media is built, tracked, and optimised.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
