&lt;p class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot; data-start=&quot;610&quot; data-end=&quot;721&quot;&gt;A digitally fluent problem solver who’s curious about how media actually works beneath the surface.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;723&quot; data-end=&quot;1022&quot;&gt;You’re confident working with data and platforms, and you enjoy connecting the dots between media performance, audience behaviour, and measurement. While you understand SEM, paid social and digital analytics, you’re most interested in how these channels integrate into a wider, smarter media system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1024&quot; data-end=&quot;1273&quot;&gt;You’re comfortable questioning setups, improving tracking, and finding better ways to measure impact. You collaborate well with strategists, creatives and media teams, and you’re motivated by making media more efficient, accountable and intelligent.&lt;/p&gt;
